 observe\nthe appearance of excess emission on the immediate interiors of cluster pairs\nas a result of asymmetric, `radio relic'-like shocks surrounding cluster cores,\nwhilst the excess emission spanning the intracluster region -- attributable to\nfilaments proper -- is two orders of magnitude lower and undetectable in our\nexperiment even under ideal conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2021 08:46:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 May 2022 06:39:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-08"}
