\Omega\\times(0,T)$, where $\\Omega\\subset{\\mathbb R}^n$ is a smooth domain.\nFinally, we use our Liouville theorems to prove universal estimates for\nparticular parabolic systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2021 10:06:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
