ern side\nof the target for UNADW than for LNADW. For UNADW, the average expected\nduration of the pathways from the Labrador and Irminger Seas was found to be of\n2 to 3 years. For LNADW, the duration was found to be influenced by the\nReykjanes Ridge, being as long as 8 years from the western side of the ridge\nand of about 3 years on average from its eastern side.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2021 11:56:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 17:39:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
